    "statement": "\\text{Under } \\mathbb{E}[\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}]=\\mathbf{0},\\, \\mathrm{Var}(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon})=\\sigma^2 I,\\text{ OLS is BLUE}",
